Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又回到 这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 什 么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber小姐回国了 真的很突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长就不必在晚上出门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经 不会再遇到危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我陪着Saber冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是我让Saber陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我可能会更常出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以后就算我回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要站在门口等我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 还没結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须打倒的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在这座镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央公园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个影子似的东西 到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和脏砚的关系也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被脏砚使役着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该只是被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得去问问远坂才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捏 我捏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你还活着呢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把名字 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥的名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是士郎啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等 让你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是敌人吗 伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我伊莉雅就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御主们只能在晚上战斗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来和士郎聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前一上来就給了我一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说要聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 这不是一回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪士郎那么弱 还非要跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是现在 我也能杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀没了Saber的士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒钟都不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你陪我说句话也没什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那伊莉雅你现在住在森林的城堡里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉和莉兹也和我住在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是好不容易躲过了塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专程跑来见士郎你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好引以为傲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再问一句可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对卫宫切嗣这个名字有印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个名字 没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 我也正想找卫宫谈点事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要谈话的话在学校里谈不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 去沏杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛那副表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么昵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们来开始作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去准备晚饭才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不早点说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是远坂让我插不上话才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放了樱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会杀掉卫宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想给他点苦头尝尝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来做Rider的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以考虑放了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是为了战斗才来这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不应该一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 怎么回事 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么简单就倒下了可是很无聊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的忍耐力 已经为你带来了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 不用再放水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样杀了他 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 把这家伙干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远 远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卫宫缔结了同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也只是一直在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你利用了樱那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就已经是我的敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 樱 樱 樱 樱 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙怎么样都无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了御主的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫 快趴下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样把他们都收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家的血统已经衰败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再会产生会使用魔术的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为是脏砚召唤了Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后转让給慎二使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 事实上並沒有这么复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的间桐家里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最适合当御主的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家正统的继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一代的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令咒的转让
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用令咒命令了Rider听从间桐慎二的指令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 慎二成为了Rider的御主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这期间 你失去了作为御主的权限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沦落为了普通的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看着哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为令咒是间桐家发明的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能够使出这种花招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把支配权让给我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还装什么乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令咒还剩下一划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二 如果令咒用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 就算再造出一本伪臣之书 也马上就会烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用借来的令咒去控制Rider的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从最开始就不是御主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道这种破办法是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我 杷他们都宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你没有遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明说了不会杀了学长的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她还控制不好能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不小心让她吸收了魔力的话 她就没法恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走开 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的主子已经失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去 她就会耗尽魔力 等于是在自毁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要吸收的魔力比消耗掉的魔力多就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 主子易改 本性难移啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是为了做这些事 才召唤你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法服从这个命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 您的生命优先于一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧 石化魔眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:22:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.16,0:23:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.96,0:23:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐樱的治疗也刚好完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和Rider一起把你们带到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮礼 樱的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且留住了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你的魔术刻印怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了治疗间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.44,0:24:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已 全部用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.65,0:24:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 此次治疗的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印虫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当是活的魔术回路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.80,0:25:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被刻印虫啃噬
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.13,0:25:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就会渗透到身体的各个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.01,0:25:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命榨取生命的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.68,0:25:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用粘液刺激皮肤 并浸润它
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令快乐中枢高扬 从而使其崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此来满足它们的饥饿感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.57,0:25:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.19,0:25:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这些虫豸浸淫的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.41,0:25:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论身体还是精神
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.66,0:25:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会遭到刻印虫的侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.62,0:25:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它们破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.29,0:25:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而间桐樱也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.75,0:25:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.67,0:25:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得需要说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.01,0:25:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要刻印虫还在体内
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:25:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为生命能量的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.34,0:26:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被无止境地吸干
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,置之不顾的话 她会死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.85,0:26:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术不是成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.60,0:26:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非全部驱除
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.15,0:26:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是积攒了11年的份
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.44,0:26:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强行驱除的话 身体会先受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把刻印虫完全驱除
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.62,0:26:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种难如登天的事 只有借助圣杯的力量才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.88,0:26:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.81,0:26:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为冬木的管理者 就由我来处置她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.65,0:26:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处置 你是说间桐樱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.86,0:27:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不能控制自己的力量的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.24,0:27:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能放她活路的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.78,0:27:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子已经是 失控的御主了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她是自己的亲妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.96,0:27:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.30,0:27:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂家本来就有两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是魔术师家族注定一脉相承
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.15,0:27:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我继承了远坂家的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.90,0:27:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱则作为血脉已经断绝的间桐
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.99,0:27:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是玛奇里家的后继者
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.32,0:27:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被收作养女
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.66,0:27:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.45,0:27:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和樱确实是亲姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.66,0:27:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说从未以姐妹相称过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.63,0:27:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.34,0:27:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就更不能
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.47,0:28:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样放着她不管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.68,0:28:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会发生同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就会毫无差别地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.52,0:28:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把无辜的人们卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.03,0:28:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要杀掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我输给樱了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.82,0:29:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这个给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.14,0:29:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我 第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从最重要的人手里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下了珍贵的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要赶在远坂之前找到她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.06,0:30:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了樱以后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.81,0:30:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.19,0:30:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.03,0:30:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上不是要战斗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.54,0:30:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正士郎已经不算是御主啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.96,0:30:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.58,0:30:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider的御主倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.92,0:30:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就剩下两个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.05,0:30:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎虽然想救Rider的御主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.43,0:30:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在就是找不到她人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.86,0:31:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 都要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.90,0:31:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 你不生我的气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.07,0:31:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会生气的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.95,0:31:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是士郎的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.95,0:31:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.09,0:31:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上说的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.88,0:31:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣的事 其实我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.05,0:31:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是为了赢得圣杯战争才诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.14,0:31:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是伊莉雅的目的一直都是杀死切嗣和士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是士郎说 想要保护自己重要的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.40,0:31:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是 士郎的同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.82,0:31:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护自己喜欢的人是理所当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.49,0:31:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.82,0:32:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的已经完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.78,0:32:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.91,0:32:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.47,0:32:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.43,0:32:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.68,0:33:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的感冒还没好透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.14,0:33:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的这个药水
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.98,0:33:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是什么毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是让感官更加敏感的药物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.20,0:33:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅如此 我就控制不了自已了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.16,0:33:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还伤害了学长
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没伤到
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是那种程度的话 我完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.71,0:33:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是间桐家的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.04,0:33:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我一直都瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.84,0:33:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 都没跟樱说自己成了御主的事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.59,0:33:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去学长家里也是因为我不敢忤逆爷爷罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.64,0:33:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用帮学长的忙当借口 一直在欺骗着学长
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.11,0:33:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直 一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.44,0:33:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不配陪在学长的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.91,0:34:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这种事就到今天为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就当你是不认识的人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.46,0:34:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在走廊里遇到也不去打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.67,0:34:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后也装成是陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.42,0:34:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地一个人回到家里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.55,0:34:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把迄今为止的事都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.43,0:34:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.18,0:34:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想自杀的时候把小刀抵在手腕上还可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是欺骗学长
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.11,0:34:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是停止这样的生活 我都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.36,0:34:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围全是可怕的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.57,0:34:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经一步都动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.87,0:34:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不知道该怎么办才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.66,0:34:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想继续守护和学长在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 对我来说明明只有那才是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命睢一的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.31,0:35:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.82,0:35:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.36,0:35:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想让她不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.41,0:35:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使谁都不责怪樱 樱也拼命自责的话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.12,0:35:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会伸手 将她拉出阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.13,0:35:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果其他人不原谅樱
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.02,0:35:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就代替樱 原谅她自己
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.57,0:35:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.07,0:36:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.49,0:36:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱是个坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.24,0:36:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会像刚刚那样暴走失控
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.58,0:36:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有一天会做出无法挽回的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.42,0:36:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我 还能有什么容身之处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.60,0:36:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 就是樱的家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.82,0:36:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.11,0:36:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不是处女了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.95,0:36:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就有了第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.12,0:36:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.29,0:36:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后又一直被好多奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把身体摸了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.04,0:37:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里还有资格让学长保护
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.85,0:37:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.77,0:37:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算樱自己想杀死自己
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.02,0:37:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会保护樱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.48,0:37:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.57,0:37:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做樱一个人的正义使者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊学长
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.08,0:37:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样肯定会让学长受到伤害的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.26,0:37:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明会让你受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.10,0:37:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.96,0:38:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.71,0:38:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.42,0:38:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.07,0:38:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是在保护至今为止的信念的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.04,0:38:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无妨 结局已能揭晓
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 若你选择了不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.34,0:39:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎便没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.09,0:39:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 可是会失去一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.61,0:39:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了吧 好好体息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.16,0:39:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发烧了吗 刚刚淋了这么久的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.83,0:39:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.05,0:39:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力有一点点 不太够
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.59,0:39:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我能帮你点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.76,0:39:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.48,0:40:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.77,0:40:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.23,0:40:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 给我一点血就好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.74,0:40:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.99,0:40:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.75,0:40:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.86,0:40:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.53,0:40:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.96,0:41:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.14,0:41:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.60,0:41:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.89,0:41:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能沾污了学长
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 帮我把做一下出汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.88,0:41:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菠菜要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.35,0:42:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就用芝麻拌一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.06,0:42:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 帮我拿个鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.18,0:42:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.19,0:42:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.66,0:42:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很久没有这样一起吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.95,0:42:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.46,0:42:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不先吃起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.75,0:42:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.92,0:42:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从者不需要像你们这样摄取营养
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.97,0:42:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 Saber倒是吃得很欢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.64,0:42:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太习惯你们的吃法
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.86,0:42:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 这个简单
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.04,0:43:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于今后的行动方针
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让樱获胜 让她使用圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.54,0:43:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得 樱还是待在家里不要出去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.63,0:43:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接和脏砚见面太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.93,0:43:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.26,0:43:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你打算如何打倒那个魔术师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.60,0:43:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得必须和其他御主联手
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.77,0:43:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有哪些御主可以合作昵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.99,0:43:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂的Archer 樱的Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.37,0:43:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赃砚手下有Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.87,0:43:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就是伊莉雅的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.62,0:43:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.84,0:43:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.26,0:43:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.72,0:44:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱不要出家门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.48,0:44:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.86,0:44:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在后悔也来不及了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 要是学长陷入危险 就把他带回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.99,0:44:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.54,0:44:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得比起那位长者
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.16,0:44:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们更应该去提防那个神父
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.13,0:44:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 实际上我也是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你放心吧 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.06,0:44:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个人 根本贏不了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.73,0:44:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.48,0:45:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学 长
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.88,0:46:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 不让他出门就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.22,0:46:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 就再也不会碰到危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.02,0:46:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.80,0:46:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是路途艰险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.02,0:47:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让我跟着它走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.24,0:47:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.67,0:47:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会掉在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.17,0:48:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的主人很像
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.51,0:48:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个懦弱的从者
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.93,0:48:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全感受不到要和我们战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.72,0:48:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命就这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.02,0:48:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.32,0:48:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望便是不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.65,0:48:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我这身体
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.41,0:48:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每时每刻都在腐烂着
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.12,0:48:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着腐臭
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.66,0:48:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长年积累的智慧正在流失
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.62,0:48:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.00,0:48:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活生生地腐烂下去的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.50,0:48:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种小辈能明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.59,0:48:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上没有不畏惧死亡的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.34,0:48:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能实现我的愿望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.27,0:49:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把全世界的人一个一个杀光 我也下得去手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.36,0:49:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你彻底失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.74,0:49:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经彻底遗忘了你的目标了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.28,0:49:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛奇里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.24,0:49:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回想起我们的夙愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奇迹的渴望来自于何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.75,0:49:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.13,0:49:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才以人类之身向非人境界前进的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.64,0:49:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人偶 也能说出这番话
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.98,0:49:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是把祖先的言行也填装进躯体里了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.77,0:49:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿戏就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.49,0:49:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦的圣杯 就由我间桐脏砚来收下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.44,0:50:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能过去 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.17,0:50:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂 你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.13,0:51:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到 卫宫和我不谋而合了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.54,0:51:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.77,0:51:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怏从那里离开
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.56,0:51:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它拖下去的话就回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.50,0:52:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.21,0:52:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.04,0:52:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别白白把爱因兹贝伦的小姑娘放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.64,0:52:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.98,0:52:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.94,0:52:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.17,0:52:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.76,0:53:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.60,0:53:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.49,0:53:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.52,0:54:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.91,0:54:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正统的英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.45,0:54:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法抵御它的咒层界的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.54,0:54:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你 已经和林中彷徨的怨灵没什么区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.11,0:54:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.91,0:54:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.99,0:54:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.00,0:54:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:55:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker！
