Comment: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（(胜利之剑,Morgan)）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H80&}（胜利之剑）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.07,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H80&\fs38\pos(960,1005)}Morgan
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.60,0:58:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.90,0:59:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经完成了我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.27,0:59:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下就交给阁下了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.90,0:59:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.32,0:59:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能弥补之前的狼狈了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.16,0:59:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.76,1:00:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.61,1:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.28,1:00:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.66,1:00:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.46,1:00:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.42,1:00:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不偷袭的话 连毛孩子都杀不掉吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.71,1:00:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.84,1:00:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.09,1:00:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还能到这里
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.39,1:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道昵
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.93,1:00:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.68,1:00:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.60,1:00:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个追上来了的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.03,1:01:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨论留在后面
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.53,1:01:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来 小子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.53,1:01:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已经牵起了伊莉雅的手
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.74,1:01:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么直到最后一刻为止都要保护好她
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.75,1:01:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.23,1:01:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.49,1:01:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还能动
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.03,1:01:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.24,1:01:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和其他英灵不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.12,1:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么能被称为「英雄」的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.66,1:01:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是什么正统的英灵
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.71,1:01:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也因此 能和些许污秽共存
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.00,1:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.08,1:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本身就是扭曲的英灵啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.15,1:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.70,1:02:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以变回灵体了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.41,1:02:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间从这里
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.87,1:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.70,1:02:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.75,1:02:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.05,1:02:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.05,1:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.89,1:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点跑啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.89,1:02:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.28,1:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力正在聚集
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.78,1:03:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.45,1:03:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来 远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.59,1:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am the bone of my sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.63,1:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Steel is my body.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.56,1:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have created
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.14,1:03:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,over a thousand blades.
Comment: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(炽天覆七重圆环,Rho        Aias)
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炽天覆七重圆环
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.19,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(960,1005)}Rho        Aias
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.65,1:04:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.62,1:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.83,1:04:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.75,1:04:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.92,1:04:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.93,1:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要保重啊 远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.28,1:05:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.96,1:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做的话你也会
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.17,1:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想都不用想
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.63,1:05:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不做的话两个人都会死
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.22,1:05:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做的话确保有一个人活下来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.94,1:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.65,1:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.24,1:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包成这样确实挺吓人的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.08,1:06:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 只是受了点小伤而已
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.54,1:06:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然缠了一圈又一圈的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.00,1:06:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很严重
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.67,1:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.92,1:06:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 远坂是我在那边遇到的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.38,1:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她救了我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.89,1:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以暂时停战了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.51,1:06:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 这位是伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.39,1:06:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 虽然很突然
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.27,1:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.36,1:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂 能动吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.15,1:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.32,1:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.91,1:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人类移植从者的身体
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.66,1:06:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事也太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.95,1:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.21,1:06:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕一次 只要使用了这只手臂的话
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.42,1:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer的魔术回路就会启动
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.13,1:06:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 你的身体无法承受
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.13,1:06:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行使魔术带来的负担
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.34,1:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会从内部开始崩坏
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.97,1:06:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这布是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.68,1:07:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是封印
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.48,1:07:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.98,1:07:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 干嘛 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就打算在打倒间桐脏砚之前要和你联手的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.15,1:07:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 能在樱身边
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.86,1:07:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是正合我意
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.12,1:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在为樱着想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.17,1:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 说得不对
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.56,1:07:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是4年前吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.94,1:07:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直练习助跑跳高练到傍晚对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.95,1:08:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不可能成功
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.53,1:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还一直在跳 真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.66,1:08:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就那样站着 傻傻地对着你这个笨蛋看了很久
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.21,1:08:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果觉得自己做不到的话
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.63,1:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很果断地放弃的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.96,1:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从根本上就是个很冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.97,1:08:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 毕竟我也是个魔术师嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.93,1:08:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时正想着「我的人生就这样继续下去真的好吗」
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.93,1:08:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这种时候 看到了和自己完全相反的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.77,1:08:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时还挺受刺激的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.62,1:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抢走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.54,1:08:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要连这份回忆都抢走啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.60,1:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.91,1:09:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这布揭开以后一看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.33,1:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经恢复原样了也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.56,1:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这样
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.98,1:09:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.53,1:10:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.58,1:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情想问你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.33,1:10:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱的幸福 就是你活着 并陪伴在她身边
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.63,1:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不期盼其他的任何事了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.59,1:10:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望她能一直活着
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.97,1:10:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.22,1:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢她啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.19,1:10:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.65,1:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是樱的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.90,1:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论未来发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.49,1:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一直是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.33,1:10:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.33,1:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.17,1:11:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是魔力不足了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.38,1:11:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来等着吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.39,1:11:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美工刀在哪里来着
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.42,1:11:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.13,1:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.85,1:11:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会保护我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.64,1:11:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.40,1:12:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我更想让樱待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.19,1:12:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要樱
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.65,1:12:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分别这种事 想都不敢想
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.16,1:12:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想让我作为家人待在身边
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.08,1:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.25,1:12:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为女孩子 待在身边呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.30,1:12:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.51,1:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢樱
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.56,1:12:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.14,1:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.40,1:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.95,1:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.74,1:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很脏吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.87,1:12:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.08,1:13:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仅仅是进了学长的房间
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.33,1:13:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已經这样了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.63,1:13:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我自己动手自慰
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.84,1:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也完全压抑不住这种欲望
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.47,1:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子里已经无法思考学长以外的事了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.51,1:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此肮脏的我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.69,1:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.36,1:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不肮脏
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.94,1:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.95,1:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.69,1:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 真是没用
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.56,1:14:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚姐姐把学长带走了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.49,1:14:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅如此 我就害怕的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.01,1:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.55,1:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.10,1:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.57,1:14:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.37,1:15:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.25,1:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.76,1:15:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.68,1:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.02,1:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.31,1:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福正在成形的另一个圣杯
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.86,1:15:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正孕育着 被称为「此世间全部之恶」的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.57,1:15:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由人类产生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.03,1:15:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人类又对其避之不及的某样东西
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.91,1:15:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善恶之所在
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.37,1:15:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是给出回答
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.46,1:15:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是生下能够给出回答的东西的话
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.92,1:15:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.26,1:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案马上就要揭晓了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.76,1:16:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说这些问题是对于神的冒渎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.76,1:16:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我便在神面前 全心全意地
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.52,1:16:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我主问倒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.40,1:16:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始要承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.99,1:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少早饭就让我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.58,1:16:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去帮远坂学姐的忙了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.38,1:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.30,1:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.30,1:16:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你对远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.39,1:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.31,1:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我先把这边的蔬菜洗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.27,1:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那就拜托
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.32,1:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 这么叫很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.37,1:17:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.33,1:17:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并 并 并没 没有什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.97,1:17:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 那件事能在我房间里做吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.60,1:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.85,1:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边 也是需要一两件秘密兵器的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.23,1:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer的手臂里
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.82,1:17:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是有着艾因兹贝伦的研究成果的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.44,1:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和远坂说 一起看看有没有办法活用这个成果
Comment: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我对(基修亚·泽尔里奇,宝石翁)留下的东西没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我对基修亚·泽尔里奇留下的东西没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:50.91,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(816,1005)}宝石翁
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.29,1:17:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得 魔法使留下的宝箱
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.67,1:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会很美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.05,1:18:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基修亚·泽尔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.55,1:18:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.80,1:18:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.64,1:18:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.35,1:18:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.94,1:18:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都只是在远处眺望着
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.11,1:18:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到真的会有
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.23,1:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能叫她「姐姐」的一天
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.53,1:18:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从到了间桐家之后
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.66,1:18:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有与远坂见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.78,1:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.24,1:18:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是我还是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.16,1:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是互相知道
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.96,1:18:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是自己的姐妹这个事实
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.83,1:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相交流什么的 是在极力避免的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.67,1:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.92,1:18:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果姐姐知道了我的魔术的话
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.64,1:18:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会讨厌我的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.55,1:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被远坂讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.56,1:18:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.27,1:18:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家的魔术
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.06,1:19:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始 就只是为了从人身上夺取某些东西而使用的魔术
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.03,1:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一味地夺取
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.78,1:19:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个不会让人喜欢的魔术
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.28,1:19:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 你讨厌间桐家的魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.29,1:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是非常严厉的教学方式
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.38,1:19:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但光论辛苦程度的话 是比不上学长的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.30,1:19:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是见过的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.97,1:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晚上 学长是多么辛苦地训练着
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.72,1:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经有很多次想阻止学长
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.94,1:19:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长的锻炼是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.11,1:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是 自己刺穿自己的喉咙一样
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.74,1:19:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是被他人强迫进行这种训练
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.24,1:19:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是独自一人固执地坚持着
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.25,1:20:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们之间 学长一定是最厉害的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.92,1:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为魔术特性
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.30,1:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因为学长的内心纯正
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.94,1:20:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第一次遇见的时候 我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.40,1:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人一定 不会背叛任何事物
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.20,1:20:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫 是你 夺走的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.90,1:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 什么反应都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.26,1:21:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这里
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.22,1:21:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂草变黑了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.18,1:21:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 是那个黑影干的 是受脏砚指使的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.56,1:21:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说 我不认为他会留下这些证据
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.03,1:21:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 没有味道
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.79,1:22:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真温暖
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.04,1:22:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 还能感觉到温度
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.80,1:22:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻能一直持续下去该多好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.18,1:23:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜静的散步
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.01,1:23:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇晃的脑袋空白一片
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.89,1:23:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标满满但心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.15,1:23:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微微抖动着 向前走
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.86,1:23:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻声哼唱着 向前走
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.57,1:23:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干枯的手脚像纸气球 滚落在地
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.24,1:23:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到长大成人 才能轻飘飘地飞起来
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.04,1:23:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前走 向前走 向前走
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.12,1:24:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎歧嘎吱 有人走了过来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.87,1:24:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只听见 哈哈大笑声
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.87,1:24:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有 感到过害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.52,1:24:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叽叽喳喳 太吵闹
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.28,1:24:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子开始 咕咕叫
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.92,1:24:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够卖力的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.42,1:24:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那时候我说了让你去死了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.94,1:25:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发光 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.33,1:25:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缓刑期结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.04,1:25:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当这是我对你的慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.89,1:25:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.11,1:26:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到不只是影子 连身体都已经产生了变化
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.72,1:26:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想让本王跪下
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.84,1:27:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.24,1:27:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到 已经到了到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.69,1:28:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.74,1:28:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.39,1:28:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.56,1:28:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上到客厅来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.71,1:29:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.00,1:29:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 我马上拿治疗道具来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.63,1:29:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.60,1:29:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发现 快停下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.28,1:29:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去想 「相似」什么的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.75,1:29:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.76,1:29:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.80,1:29:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.64,1:30:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.64,1:30:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱的身体 只是看上去完好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.23,1:30:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上手脚的筋脉全都断裂破碎了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.36,1:30:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 绝对已经死过一次了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.57,1:30:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不知道谁是凶手
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.37,1:30:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不只是身体上的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.41,1:30:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的大脑可能也被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.16,1:30:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽快打倒赃砚和那个影子才行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.63,1:30:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 我们要尽我们所能
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.09,1:30:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.43,1:30:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一脏砚和那个黑影没有任何关系的话
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.14,1:30:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.83,1:31:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旱上好 自己的意识还在吗 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.12,1:31:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么庞大的灵魂 你是从哪里吸收到的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.54,1:31:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明Assassin和Rider都还在
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.80,1:31:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已经饱和了 真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.39,1:31:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 你知道接下来你会变成什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.27,1:31:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.44,1:31:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死的 绝对 不会得救
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.08,1:31:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 好不容易能回来看看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.29,1:31:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 士郎 不在吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.34,1:31:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.05,1:32:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 士郎跑去哪了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.89,1:32:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明现在是小樱最需要关照的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.27,1:32:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.28,1:32:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长说 会保护我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.12,1:32:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.29,1:32:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我犯的错
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.42,1:32:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长的梦想破碎了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.42,1:32:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.21,1:32:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 我是坏人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.26,1:32:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎是遇见坏人一定会斥责的人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.27,1:32:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱也想改掉自己坏的地方 对吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.78,1:32:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.19,1:33:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.20,1:33:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 士郎的梦想是要做正义的伙伴不是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.28,1:33:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想保护的人不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.25,1:33:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的话 就不应该偏袒我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.58,1:33:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎的目标是切嗣先生的话
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.09,1:33:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有重要的人也是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.30,1:33:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣先生也是个很偏心的人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.48,1:33:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个城市定居之后也是
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.40,1:33:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣先生也会一次又一次地跑去海外
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.61,1:33:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他的身体动不了为止 他一直都在这样做
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.08,1:33:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有个无论如何都要见到的人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.63,1:34:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能见到重要的人 是非常痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.09,1:34:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是正义的伙伴也是如此
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.30,1:34:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 小樱要好好陪在士郎的身边哦
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.45,1:34:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.17,1:34:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要背叛 曾经的自己吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.10,1:34:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.27,1:35:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要背叛的话 你会
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.57,1:35:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.79,1:35:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不会是这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.22,1:35:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎 对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.27,1:35:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师大人有话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.75,1:36:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中到得早啊 叫卫宫的小子
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.00,1:36:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏砚 我要说的话只有一句
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.84,1:36:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧把樱解放了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.22,1:36:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吗 这么说也行吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.69,1:36:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎 今天叫你过来 是有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.32,1:36:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你把那个黑影给杀了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.49,1:36:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的同伙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.03,1:36:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伙吗 你觉得那是能和人类交流的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.25,1:36:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚开始连安抚它都做不到了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.42,1:36:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 在那之前 得先告诉你那个黑影到底是什么东西才行
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.68,1:36:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直说了吧 那是圣杯的内在
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.56,1:37:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从被称为「圣杯」的门里溢出的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.11,1:37:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是黑影的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.99,1:37:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影和 门
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.95,1:37:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚说要你把黑影杀掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.70,1:37:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那应该是非常困难的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.25,1:37:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 把门杀掉 是做得到的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.34,1:37:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和远坂家的小姑娘想动手的话 会被发现
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.21,1:37:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓从者 也不过是饲料而已
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.18,1:37:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.35,1:37:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我种植下了圣杯的碎片
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.68,1:37:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我培养了十年的间桐家的圣杯 能把她杀掉的只有
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.40,1:37:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.07,1:37:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.20,1:37:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和樱 很相似啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.50,1:38:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把存在于那里的人偶
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.13,1:38:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借由心爱的男人之手将其终结而已
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.71,1:38:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也应该也是她的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.51,1:38:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.97,1:38:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦樱自己的意识变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.01,1:38:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿在潜意识中的圣杯意识就会浮现
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.44,1:38:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前的灾害就会重现吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.36,1:38:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想拯救樱的话
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.11,1:38:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得忍耐到圣杯战争的期限结束
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.78,1:38:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从过去的例子来看还有4天吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.29,1:38:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.58,1:38:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得樱能坚持到那个时候吗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.92,1:38:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.13,1:38:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对能坚持到那时候
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.67,1:38:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其他人类可就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.80,1:38:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为昨晚的暴食
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.34,1:39:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能现在肚子是挺饱的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.85,1:39:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 最快的话可能明天
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.27,1:39:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就会再次行动
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.94,1:39:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得需要多少天 它就会把这个城市的人吃光呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.24,1:39:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能明白
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.66,1:39:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了万人除恶
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.91,1:39:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你继承了卫宫切嗣的志向
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.66,1:39:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐樱 才是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.73,1:39:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.07,1:40:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.03,1:40:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 学长
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.06,1:41:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 这次圣杯战争结束后 有没有什么想做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.91,1:41:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 想不到有什么要做的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.29,1:41:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得只要能和学长在一起 就够了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.08,1:41:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我们一起去哪里玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.84,1:41:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.63,1:41:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我想去 赏花
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.23,1:41:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就说好咯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.25,1:42:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用被冰冻结的心 做出温暖的幻想
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.25,1:42:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待到何时冬日远去 崭新的春天来临
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.17,1:42:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你我二人 一起去赏樱花吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.45,1:42:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 等春天到来
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.62,1:42:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.54,1:43:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.55,1:43:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从十分珍视的人手中得到如此重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.18,1:43:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想继续守护和学长在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.81,1:43:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.97,1:43:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学 长
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.94,1:44:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要背叛自己吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.49,1:44:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.78,1:44:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你 学长
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.20,1:44:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从你那里得到了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.24,1:44:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.29,1:45:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能叫你姐姐 我真的是很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.75,1:45:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤村老师 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.76,1:45:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没能遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.48,1:45:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 谢谢你手下留情 没有杀死学长
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.86,1:45:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.24,1:45:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的令咒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.29,1:45:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.80,1:45:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去阻止爷爷
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.84,1:45:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能已经来不及了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.76,1:45:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能再给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.39,1:46:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.56,1:46:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.88,1:46:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 你个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.38,1:46:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来得可真够晚的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.31,1:46:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.10,1:46:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.65,1:46:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着这个试试
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.99,1:46:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是危险的玩意
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.92,1:47:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.51,1:47:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱你可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.01,1:47:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好哪天就能超过远坂了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.48,1:47:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 哥
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.08,1:47:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自大了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.29,1:47:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是我的人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.13,1:47:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又一次搞错了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.80,1:47:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会被如此残暴地对待
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.09,1:48:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 还是和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.68,1:48:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍忍耐一会儿就好
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.06,1:48:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.23,1:48:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐下去忍耐下去
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.40,1:48:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.90,1:48:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.82,1:48:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不愿意
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.41,1:48:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经是学长的人了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.83,1:48:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.04,1:48:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他把你调教得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.87,1:48:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.84,1:48:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.55,1:48:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么每次都会是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.43,1:48:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从很久以前就这样想了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.26,1:48:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在恨着他
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.85,1:48:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我所处的世界周遭
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.77,1:48:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此地嫌弃我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.61,1:49:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 要告诉卫宫才行
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.61,1:49:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止 你多少次投入我的怀中
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.50,1:49:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多么肮脏地和我做过
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.42,1:49:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人 如果不存在多好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.70,1:49:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 哥
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.30,1:50:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.82,1:55:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H15&\fs130\pos(960,750)\fad(500,1500)}下  集  预  告
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.06,1:55:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.82,1:55:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为只属于樱的正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.49,1:56:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 咬紧牙关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.39,up,NTP,0,0,0,,调查正在进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.06,up,NTP,0,0,0,,今早警方进入现场时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.31,up,NTP,0,0,0,,发现寺庙的建筑物有一部分发生了崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.32,up,NTP,0,0,0,,现在由前方发回报道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.32,up,NTP,0,0,0,,位于东木市深山町円藏山中的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.86,up,NTP,0,0,0,,柳洞寺所发生的崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.54,up,NTP,0,0,0,,如大家所见 目前已经被封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.91,up,NTP,0,0,0,,无法看到内部的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.25,up,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的建筑崩塌所涉及的建筑物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:38.21,up,NTP,0,0,0,,这座柳洞寺的崩落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.68,up,NTP,0,0,0,,是由寺内原有的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:54.17,comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{/fs:35}出汁:从鲣鱼干及晒干的海带中提取制作而成的日式调味品
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.37,1:07:27.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 这是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.54,1:07:32.34,up,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我要是没有成为御主的话
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.84,1:07:34.67,up,NTP,0,0,0,,也就不会认识远坂了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.97,1:07:43.85,up,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎样我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.22,1:07:47.48,up,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很早之前就知道你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.49,1:08:00.49,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时也在现场
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.75,1:21:26.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.29,1:21:32.09,up,NTP,0,0,0,,在东木市新都的中央公园发现了疑似被杀害的人的遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.63,1:21:33.72,up,NTP,0,0,0,,被害者有四人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.30,1:21:38.10,up,NTP,0,0,0,,在公园的长椅上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.51,1:21:39.56,up,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了遗体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.19,1:28:48.36,up,NTP,0,0,0,,本日22点30分左右新都站周边发生了大规模停电
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.15,1:28:54.41,up,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 警方接到了大量奇怪的报案
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.87,1:28:57.70,up,NTP,0,0,0,,据称「身边的人不见了」 「下落不明」 「突然消失了」
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.82,1:29:39.66,up,NTP,0,0,0,,目前已知的被害人已超过60人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.87,1:29:45.29,up,NTP,0,0,0,,据称 已有40栋建筑中的住客全部下落不明
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.55,1:43:01.08,up,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.28,1:43:03.79,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.79,1:43:05.64,up,NTP,0,0,0,,成为正义的伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.83,1:43:06.40,up,NTP,0,0,0,,吗…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.90,1:43:06.77,up,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.10,1:43:11.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,希望这一瞬间能永远持续下去
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.45,1:51:23.26,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}请施与我怜惜
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.26,1:51:27.68,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}如同轻抚那坠落的雏鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.68,1:51:30.30,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}请赐予我悲悯
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.30,1:51:32.26,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}愿你双目含泪
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.26,1:51:33.81,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}将我俯视
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.81,1:51:36.94,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}嗟叹我何其悲惨
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.94,1:51:42.65,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}以鞋尖拨弄我亦无妨
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.65,1:51:46.40,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}愿你说着不介意我的肮脏
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.40,1:51:49.94,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}握住我满是污泥的双手
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.94,1:51:53.79,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}来吧 让我们围作一圈翩然起舞
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.79,1:51:58.29,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}让我们将碍眼的森罗万象
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.29,1:52:01.38,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}一并吞入腹中
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.38,1:52:09.13,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}佐上令人难以承受的香辛料岂不美味？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.11,1:52:28.61,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}惊惧的雏鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.61,1:52:33.20,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}无法鸣响一曲离歌
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.20,1:52:37.83,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}它乞求着爱怜 陷入沉默
