Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.72,1:55:01.72,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}那渐渐衰亡的光芒
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.72,1:55:05.10,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}亦终将照亮你的身侧
