Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.98,1:55:09.56,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}令我泪流不止
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.56,1:55:12.44,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}求你 陪在我身旁
